citon/trion transition by\nsuppressing the BL transition. The study thus creates an opportunity to use CVD\ngrown large area 1L-MoS$_2$ for the development of optoelectronic as well as\nvalleytronic devices for practical applications for the future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Apr 2022 10:44:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-09"}
