 the\npandemic period. To the best of our knowledge, this paper is the longest\nquantitative measurement of Sinophobia.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Apr 2022 15:17:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-20"}
